text: ( Source : Lawrence University ) Two new members have been elected to Lawrence University’s of Board of Trustees . Healthcare consultant Omer Sayeed and nationally recognized attorney Anton Valukas join Shelley Davis ’92, Chicago , Ill. , Dr.
